==== 生殖型 ====
生殖型包含雌蟲和雄蟲，稱作蟻后和蟻王<ref name="techreport">{{cite techreport|first1=M.A.|last1=Horwood|first2=R.H.|last2=Eldridge|title=Termites in New South Wales Part 1. Termite biology|number=96-38|institution=Forest Resources Research|year=2005|url=http://www.dpi.nsw.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/252007/Termites-Part-1--Termite-biology.pdf|issn=0155-7548|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227214345/http://www.dpi.nsw.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/252007/Termites-Part-1--Termite-biology.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，蟻后負責產卵，蟻王負責讓卵受精<ref name="Keller1998">{{cite journal|title=Queen lifespan and colony characteristics in ants and termites|first1=L.|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s000400050084|year=1998|volume=45|pages=235–246|last1=Keller}}</ref>。在某些物種中，蟻后的腹部會隨著時間膨脹，提高生殖能力，這種現象稱作「腹膨大（{{tsl|en|physogastrism||physogastrism}}）」<ref name="techreport" />。有翅生殖型會在一年中的某些特定時間出現，而這特定時間因物種而異，等到婚飛的時候來臨，有翅生殖型會傾巢而出，同時吸引大量掠食者前來<ref name="techreport" />。

[[臺灣家白蟻|台灣家白蟻]]、[[格斯特家白蟻|格斯特家白蟻]]，和[[臺灣土白蟻|台灣土白蟻]]的有翅繁殖型常會在空氣濕度高的溫暖夏夜傾巢而出，尤其是台灣土白蟻常在下過雨的夜晚婚飛，又因其具有趨光性，婚飛時常常湧入民眾家中或是光源處（路燈下），有時婚飛規模龐大，常會吸引民眾目光<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=935679|title=全台爆發大水蟻！網期待「要下雨了嗎」　鄭明典也想問專家|author=周羿彣|publisher=三立新聞網|accessdate=2021-05-07|language=中文|archive-date=2021-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209235423/https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=935679|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這類有翅繁殖型俗稱大水蟻。

生殖型可分二類：有翅型及補充生殖型，在群體中負責生殖後代。

* '''有翅型 （alate）''' 為白蟻主要的繁殖方式，又稱主要生殖型（primary reproductive）。有翅型個體生殖器官功能正常，靠飛行進行長距離移動，交配後建立新群體，成為創始蟻王蟻后，在某些白蟻（如[[臺灣土白蟻|台灣土白蟻]]）中，蟻后的卵巢會隨著時間漸漸發育，導致腹部膨大。

* '''補充生殖型 （neotenic）'''為有翅型以外的具有繁殖能力的個體，又稱次要生殖型（secondary reproductive） 。可粗分為短翅型 （brachypterous） 與無翅型 （apterous），在某些物種中可以在創建群體的有翅型死後填補生殖的功能，如[[黃原鼻白蟻|黃原鼻白蟻]]。

== 語源學 ==
Isoptera 源於希臘文，''Iso'' 意思為相等（equal），''Ptera'' 意思為翅膀（winged），命名由來是因為白蟻的前後翅大小幾乎相等<ref name="Bugsrule">{{cite book|last1=Cranshaw|first1=W.|title=Bugs Rule!: An Introduction to the World of Insects|date=2013|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, New Jersey|isbn=978-0-691-12495-7|page=188|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/?id=p_3c0qGP_t0C&pg=PA188&lpg=PA188&dq=Etymology+of+termite#v=onepage&q=Etymology%20of%20termite&f=false|chapter=11}}</ref>。Termite 為晚期拉丁文，是[[卡尔·林奈|林奈]]於1781年創造的拉丁詞彙<ref>{{cite web|title=Termite|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/termite?show=0&t=1420442739|accessdate=5 January 2015|publisher=Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411182013/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/termite?show=0&t=1420442739|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和 ''terere''（摩擦、耗損、侵蝕）有關，源於早期拉丁文的 ''tarmes 。''蟻巢稱作 ''terminarium'' 或 ''termitaria <ref name="termitety">{{OEtymD|Termite}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Lobeck|first1=A. Kohl|title=Geomorphology; an Introduction to the Study of Landscapes|date=1939|publisher=McGraw Hill Book Company, Incorporated|location=University of California|pages=431–432|edition=1st|asin=B002P5O9SC}}</ref>''。在早期的英文中，白蟻稱作 wood ants 或 white ants <ref name="termitety" />。

在[[德语|德語]]中，白蟻又稱「{{lang|de|Unglückshafte}}」，意為“带有厄運的動物”或“帶來不幸的動物”。

法語：Formic de blanc，意思為白蟻。

英語：White ant，意思為白蟻。

中文：白蟻。

== 分類學與演化 ==
[[File:Mastotermes_darwiniensis.jpg|替代=The giant northern termite is the most primitive living termite. Its body plan has been described as a cockroach's abdomen stuck to a termite's fore part. Its wings have the same form as roach wings, and like roaches, it lays its eggs in a case.]]的形態推論白蟻和蟑螂親緣關係接近。]]
白蟻舊時被分作等翅目（Isoptera），但後來根據分子生物學證據將白蟻併入蜚蠊目。

Cleveland 於1934年發現白蟻和[[隱尾蠊屬|隱尾蠊]]的腸內具有類似的[[鞭毛蟲|原生生物]]，推論白蟻和隱尾蠊親緣關係接近<ref>{{cite journal|title=The Wood-Feeding Roach ''Cryptocercus'', its protozoa, and the symbiosis between protozoa and roach|first1=L.R.|last2=Hall|first2=S.K.|date=1934|journal=Memoirs of the American Academy of Arts and Sciences|issue=2|doi=10.1093/aesa/28.2.216|volume=17|pages=185–382|last3=Sanders|first3=E.P.|last4=Collier|first4=J.|last1=Cleveland}}</ref>。McKittrick F. A. 於1965年提到某些白蟻和隱尾蠊若蟲具有相似特徵，進一步支持了白蟻和隱尾蠊接近的假說<ref>{{cite journal|title=A contribution to the understanding of cockroach-termite affinities.|first1=F.A.|date=1965|journal=Annals of the Entomological Society of America|issue=1|doi=10.1093/aesa/58.1.18|volume=58|pages=18–22|pmid=5834489|last1=McKittrick}}</ref>。2008 年根據 16S rRNA 的 DNA 分析結果支持白蟻於演化樹上的位置被包覆在蜚蠊目之中<ref>{{cite journal|title=Relationships among the major lineages of Dictyoptera: the effect of outgroup selection on dictyopteran tree topology|first1=J.L.|last2=Litman|first2=J.|date=2008|journal=Systematic Entomology|issue=3|doi=10.1111/j.1365-3113.2008.00424.x|volume=33|pages=429–450|last3=Klass|first3=K.-D.|last4=Spearman|first4=L.A.|last1=Ware}}</ref><ref name="inward">{{cite journal|title=Death of an order: a comprehensive molecular phylogenetic study confirms that termites are eusocial cockroaches.|first1=D.|last2=Beccaloni|first2=G.|date=2007|journal=Biology Letters|issue=3|doi=10.1098/rsbl.2007.0102|volume=3|pages=331–5|pmc=2464702|pmid=17412673|last3=Eggleton|first3=P.|last1=Inward}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Response to Lo ''et al.''|first1=P.|last2=Beccaloni|first2=G.|date=2007|journal=Biology Letters|issue=5|doi=10.1098/rsbl.2007.0367|volume=3|pages=564–565|pmc=2391203|last3=Inward|first3=D.|last1=Eggleton}}</ref>。隱尾蠊屬和白蟻為[[姐妹群|姊妹群]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Inheritance and diversification of symbiotic trichonymphid flagellates from a common ancestor of termites and the cockroach ''Cryptocercus''|first1=M.|last2=Noda|first2=S.|date=2009|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|issue=1655|doi=10.1098/rspb.2008.1094|volume=276|pages=239–245|pmc=2674353|pmid=18812290|last3=Hongoh|first3=Y.|last4=Nalepa|first4=C.A.|last5=Inoue|first5=T.|last1=Ohkuma}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Evidence from multiple gene sequences indicates that termites evolved from wood-feeding cockroaches|first1=N.|last2=Tokuda|first2=G.|date=June 2000|journal=Current Biology|issue=13|doi=10.1016/S0960-9822(00)00561-3|volume=10|pages=801–814|pmid=10898984|last3=Watanabe|first3=H.|last4=Rose|first4=H.|last5=Slaytor|first5=M.|last6=Maekawa|first6=K.|last7=Bandi|first7=C.|last8=Noda|first8=H.|last1=Lo}}</ref>，白蟻和隱尾蠊的形態和行為都有相似之處，如：大多蜚蠊沒有社會性，但隱尾蠊會育幼，甚至還會交哺和社會性梳理<ref>{{cite book|title=Evolution of the insects|url=https://archive.org/details/evolutioninsects00grim|last1=Grimaldi|first1=D.|last2=Engel|first2=M.S.|date=2005|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0-521-82149-0|edition=1st|location=Cambridge|page=[https://archive.org/details/evolutioninsects00grim/page/n251 237]}}</ref>。有學者認為白蟻是從隱尾蠊演化而來<ref name="inward" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Wood-feeding cockroaches as models for termite evolution (Insecta: Dictyoptera): ''Cryptocercus'' vs. ''Parasphaeria boleiriana''|first1=K.D.|last2=Nalepa|first2=C.|date=2008|journal=Molecular Phylogenetics & Evolution|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2007.11.028|volume=46|pages=809–817|pmid=18226554|last3=Lo|first3=N.|last1=Klass}}</ref>，有些學者把白蟻分在白蟻上科（Termitoidae）中，白蟻上科中包含白蟻和隱尾蠊屬<ref>{{cite journal|title=Comment. Save Isoptera: a comment on Inward ''et al.''|first1=N.|last2=Engel|first2=M.S.|date=2007|journal=Biology Letters|issue=5|doi=10.1098/rsbl.2007.0264|volume=3|pages=562–563|pmc=2391185|pmid=17698448|last3=Cameron|first3=S.|last4=Nalepa|first4=C.A.|last5=Tokuda|first5=G.|last6=Grimaldi|first6=D.|last7=Kitade|first7=O..|last8=Krishna|first8=K.|last9=Klass|first9=K.-D.|first12=G.J.|last12=Thompson|first11=T.|last11=Miura|first10=K.|last10=Maekawa|last1=Lo}}</ref>。學者認為白蟻接近蟑螂和螳螂，因此將白蟻也分入[[網翅總目|網翅總目]]中<ref name="Costa">{{cite book|title=The other insect societies|last=Costa|first=James|publisher=Harvard University Press|year=2006|isbn=978-0-674-02163-1|pages=135–136}}</ref><ref name="cap2008">{{cite book|title=Encyclopedia of Entomology|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaento00capi_189|last1=Capinera|first1=J.L.|date=2008|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-1-4020-6242-1|edition=2nd|location=Dordrecht|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaento00capi_189/page/n3096 3033]–3037, 3754}}</ref>。
最古老的白蟻化石可追溯至白堊紀早期，但根據白堊紀白蟻的多樣性，和包裹在白堊紀化石中的共生原生動物，部分學者推測白蟻起源的年代可能是[[侏罗紀|侏罗紀]]或[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Termites (Isoptera) from the Jurassic/Cretaceous boundary: Evidence for the longevity of their earliest genera|first1=P.|last2=Aristov|first2=D.|date=2014|journal=European Journal of Entomology|issue=1|doi=10.14411/eje.2014.014|volume=111|pages=137–141|last1=Vrsanky}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Description of an early Cretaceous termite (Isoptera: Kalotermitidae) and its associated intestinal protozoa, with comments on their co-evolution|first1=G.O.|date=2009|journal=Parasites & Vectors|issue=1–17|doi=10.1186/1756-3305-2-12|volume=2|pages=12|pmc=2669471|pmid=19226475|last1=Poinar}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Phylogeny of Dictyoptera: Dating the Origin of Cockroaches, Praying Mantises and Termites with Molecular Data and Controlled Fossil Evidence|first1=F.|last2=Nel|first2=A.|date=2015|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=7|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0130127|volume=10|pages=e0130127|bibcode=2015PLoSO..1030127L|pmc=4511787|pmid=26200914|last3=Svenson|first3=G.J.|last4=Robillard|first4=T.|last5=Pellens|first5=R.|last6=Grandcolas|first6=P.|last7=Escriva|first7=H.|last1=Legendre}}</ref>。扶魯塔食蟻獸（''{{tsl|en|Fruitafossor||Fruitafossor}}'' ） 形態類似於現代專食白蟻的哺乳類<ref>{{cite journal|title=A Late Jurassic digging mammal and early mammalian diversification.|first1=Z.X.|last2=Wible|first2=J.R.|date=2005|journal=Science|issue=5718|doi=10.1126/science.1108875|volume=308|pages=103–107|bibcode=2005Sci...308..103L|pmid=15802602|last1=Luo}}</ref>，科學家推測其專食白蟻，它的生存年代為晚侏罗世，學者因此推測白蟻起源於侏罗紀。最古老的白蟻巢年代為晚侏罗世，地點為德州西部，最古老的糞球也發現於德州西部<ref>{{cite journal|title=Oldest termite nest from the Upper Cretaceous of west Texas|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_geology_1986-01_14_1/page/87|first1=D.M.|last2=Boucot|first2=A. J.|journal=Geology|issue=1|doi=10.1130/0091-7613(1986)14<87:OTNFTU>2.0.CO;2|year=1986|volume=14|pages=87|bibcode=1986Geo....14...87R|last3=Miller|first3=J.|last4=Abbott|first4=M.|last1=Rohr}}</ref>。若試圖將白蟻起源推得更早，可能會面臨爭議，如：Weesner F. M. 曾指出[[澳白蟻科|澳白蟻科]]的起源可追溯至晚二疊世，也就是2億5千萬年前<ref name="#1"/>，同時，堪薩斯州的二疊紀沉積層中出土了類似於澳白蟻屬的翅膀化石<ref name="Tilyard">{{cite journal|title=Kansas Permian insects. Part XX the cockroaches, or order Blattaria|first1=R.J.|date=1937|journal=American Journal of Science|issue=201|doi=10.2475/ajs.s5-34.201.169|volume=34|pages=169–202, 249–276|bibcode=1937AmJS...34..169T|last1=Tilyard}}</ref>。白蟻的起源甚至可追溯至石炭紀<ref>{{cite book|last1=Henry|first1=M.S.|title=Symbiosis: Associations of Invertebrates, Birds, Ruminants, and Other Biota|date=2013|publisher=Elsevier|location=New York, New York|isbn=978-1-4832-7592-5|page=59}}</ref>。[[木蜚蠊|木蜚蠊]] ''Pycnoblattina'' 的翅膀與澳白蟻相似，現代的昆蟲中只有澳白蟻和它相似<ref name="Tilyard" />。然而 Krishna 等人（2003） 認為[[古生代|古生代]]和[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]的白蟻事實上並非白蟻，且應從等翅目中移除<ref name="Krishna, K. 2013">{{cite journal|title=Treatise on the Isoptera of the world|url=http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/bitstream/handle/2246/6430/B377%20vol.%201.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y|first1=K.|last2=Grimaldi|first2=D.A.|journal=Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History|issue=7|doi=10.1206/377.1|year=2013|series=1|volume=377|pages=1–200|last3=Krishna|first3=V.|last4=Engel|first4=M.S.|last1=Krishna|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183115/http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/bitstream/handle/2246/6430/B377%20vol.%201.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他研究推論白蟻的起源較晚，是白堊紀早期時從[[隱尾蠊屬|隱尾蠊屬]]演化而來<ref name=":02">{{Cite journal|title=An integrative phylogenomic approach illuminates the evolutionary history of cockroaches and termites (Blattodea)|url=https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rspb.2018.2076|last=Evangelista|first=Dominic A.|last2=Wipfler|first2=Benjamin|date=2019-01-30|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|issue=1895|doi=10.1098/rspb.2018.2076|volume=286|pages=20182076|language=en|issn=0962-8452|pmc=6364590|pmid=30963947|last3=Béthoux|first3=Olivier|last4=Donath|first4=Alexander|last5=Fujita|first5=Mari|last6=Kohli|first6=Manpreet K.|last7=Legendre|first7=Frédéric|last8=Liu|first8=Shanlin|last9=Machida|first9=Ryuichiro|first11=Ralph S.|last11=Peters|first10=Bernhard|last10=Misof|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183950/https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rspb.2018.2076|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
