=== 新等翅類群 ===
新等翅類群（Neoisoptera），意思為「新的白蟻」，在演化的歷史上新等翅類群是比較晚出現的類群，新等翅類群在分類位階上屬「從目（nanorder）」。新等翅類群中包含白蟻科，白蟻科沒有假工蟻（Pseudergates）。白蟻科腸道內有共生真核細菌幫助消化纖維素<ref>{{cite journal|title=High‐resolution analysis of gut environment and bacterial microbiota reveals functional compartmentation of the gut in wood‐feeding higher termites (''Nasutitermes'' spp.)|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_applied-and-environmental-microbiology_2012-07_78_13/page/4691|first1=T|last2=Dietrich|first2=C|journal=Applied and Environmental Microbiology|issue=13|doi=10.1128/aem.00683-12|year=2012|volume=78|pages=4691–4701|pmc=3370480|pmid=22544239|last3=Scheffrahn|first3=RH|last4=Brune|first4=A|last1=Kohler}}</ref>，有些物種甚至會和''{{tsl|en|Termitomyces||Termitomyces}}'' 屬的真菌共生，而低等白蟻腸道內則含有原生動物和原核細菌。

