== 分布與多樣性 ==
除[[南極洲|南極洲]]外的大陸都有紀錄。北美洲和歐洲的多樣性較低（歐洲已知10種，北美已知50種），南美洲多樣性較高，已知超過400種<ref name="tbiology">{{cite web|title=Termite Biology and Ecology|url=http://www.chem.unep.ch/pops/termites/termite_ch2.htm|accessdate=12 January 2015|work=Division of Technology, Industry and Economics Chemicals Branch|publisher=United Nations Environment Programme|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110052539/http://www.chem.unep.ch/pops/termites/termite_ch2.htm|archivedate=10 November 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>。目前已發表3000多種白蟻，其中1000多種棲息於非洲，非洲有些地區的蟻塚數量極多，光是[[克留格爾國家公園|克留格爾國家公園]]北部就有1100萬個白蟻蟻塚<ref name=":1">{{cite journal|title=Distribution and density of termite mounds in the northern Kruger National Park, with specific reference to those constructed by ''Macrotermes'' Holmgren (Isoptera: Termitidae)|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/259487863|first1=V.W.|last2=Braack|first2=L.E.O.|date=1999|journal=African Entomology|issue=1|volume=7|pages=123–130|last3=Biggs|first3=H.C.|last4=Ebersohn|first4=C.|last1=Meyer}}</ref>。亞洲有435種白蟻，大部分分布於中國長江以南的微熱帶及亞熱帶地區<ref name="tbiology" />。澳洲已知超過360種白蟻，大多是特有種<ref name="tbiology" />。

白蟻無法棲息於寒冷地區，因其表皮較柔軟<ref>{{cite journal|title=Biomass of termites and their emissions of methane and carbon dioxide: A global database|first1=M.G.|date=1996|journal=Global Biogeochemical Cycles|issue=4|doi=10.1029/96GB01893|volume=10|pages=543–557|bibcode=1996GBioC..10..543S|last1=Sanderson}}</ref>。白蟻可依棲地粗分為三類：腐木白蟻（[[原白蟻科|原白蟻科]]）、乾木白蟻（[[木白蟻科|木白蟻科]]）、地下白蟻（[[鼻白蟻科|鼻白蟻科]]），腐木白蟻棲息於針葉林，乾木白蟻棲息於闊葉林，地下白蟻則廣泛分布<ref name="tbiology" />。西印度乾木白蟻（''{{tsl|en|Cryptotermes brevis||Cryptotermes brevis}}'' ） 在澳洲是入侵種<ref name="Heather1971">{{cite journal|title=The exotic drywood termite ''Cryptotermes brevis'' (Walker) (Isoptera : Kalotermitidae) and endemic Australian drywood termites in Queensland|first1=N.W.|date=1971|journal=Australian Journal of Entomology|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1440-6055.1971.tb00022.x|volume=10|pages=134–141|last1=Heather}}</ref>。
