== 生命週期 ==
[[File:Termite-by-RalfR.jpg|替代=A termite nymph looks like a smaller version of an adult but lacks the specialisations that would enable identification of its caste.]]
白蟻常常和社會性膜翅目（螞蟻和一些蜂類）被放在一起討論，但它們的生命週期差異甚大。真社會性膜翅目的工蟲都是雌性，雄性是由未受精卵發育而來的單套體（n），雌性則是由受精卵發育而來的雙套體（2n），而白蟻的工蟻兩性皆有，且都為受精卵發育而來的雙套體（2n）。根據白蟻物種不同，雄蟲和雌蟲負責的工作可能不同<ref>{{cite journal|title=Termites, hemimetabolous diploid white ants?|first1=J.|date=2008|journal=Frontiers in Zoology|issue=1|doi=10.1186/1742-9994-5-15|volume=5|pages=15|pmc=2564920|pmid=18822181|last1=Korb}}</ref>。

白蟻的生命週期為卵、幼蟲、成蟲，這種沒有經過蛹期的生命週期稱作不完全變態<ref>{{cite web|title=Termite Identification|url=http://agspsrv34.agric.wa.gov.au/ento/termites.htm|publisher=Entomology at Western Australian Department of Agriculture|archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20090612011547/http://agspsrv34.agric.wa.gov.au/ento/termites.htm|archivedate=2009-06-12|last1=Davis|first1=P.|url-status=dead}}</ref>。幼蟲的外形類似縮小版的成蟲，它們透過蛻皮來長大，在 ''Cryptotermes dudleyi'' 中''，''幼蟲（卵孵化出的個體）會經歷四次蛻皮，而若蟲（將來會發育成有翅型的個體）會經歷三次蛻皮，最終成為有翅型<ref>{{cite journal|title=Developmental stages and caste composition of a mature and incipient colony of the drywood termite, ''Cryptotermes dudleyi'' (Isoptera: Kalotermitidae)|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-entomology_2011-04_104_2/page/622|first1=K.B.|last2=Lee|first2=C.Y.|date=2011|journal=Journal of Economic Entomology|issue=2|doi=10.1603/ec10346|volume=104|pages=622–8|pmid=21510214|last1=Neoh}}</ref>。若蟲可以透過蛻皮變成兵蟻或有翅型<ref name="uflorida">{{cite web|title=Native subterranean termites|url=http://entnemdept.ufl.edu/creatures/urban/termites/native_subterraneans.htm|accessdate=8 January 2015|publisher=University of Florida|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411182054/http://entnemdept.ufl.edu/creatures/urban/termites/native_subterraneans.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

從若蟲發育成有翅型的過程耗時數個月，具體時間會受食物多寡、氣溫、群體中個體數量影響。若蟲無法自行取食，需透過工蟻餵食，工蟻的其他工作包含覓食、建造或修繕蟻巢、照顧蟻王蟻后<ref name="aus" /><ref name="Michael">{{cite web|title=Termite Life Cycle and Caste System|url=http://www.fzi.uni-freiburg.de/InsectPestKey-long%20version/termit2.htm|accessdate=8 January 2015|date=1999|publisher=University of Freiburg|last1=Schneider|first1=M.F.|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183127/http://www.fzi.uni-freiburg.de/InsectPestKey-long%20version/termit2.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。費洛蒙調節白蟻的階級分化，讓大部分的個體無法成為繁殖階級，只有極少部分有機會生育<ref>{{cite journal|title=Polyphenism in Insects|first1=S.J.|last2=Sword|first2=G.A.|date=2011|journal=Current Biology|issue=18|doi=10.1016/j.cub.2011.06.006|volume=21|pages=738–749|pmid=21959164|last3=Lo|first3=N.|last1=Simpson}}</ref>。

''Reticulitermes speratus'' 的蟻后壽命很長，且生殖能力不會隨著時間下降。''Reticulitermes speratus'' 的蟻后所受到的[[氧化壓力|氧化壓力]]（包含氧化性 DNA 損傷，{{tsl|en|DNA oxidation||oxidative DNA damage}}）比工蟻、兵蟻和若蟲都小很多<ref name="pmid28076409">{{cite journal|title=An Efficient Antioxidant System in a Long-Lived Termite Queen|url=|date=2017|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=1|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0167412|volume=12|pages=e0167412|bibcode=2017PLoSO..1267412T|pmc=5226355|pmid=28076409|vauthors=Tasaki E, Kobayashi K, Matsuura K, Iuchi Y}}</ref>，因為這個物種的蟻后具有較多的[[过氧化氢酶|過氧化氫酶]]，過氧化氫酶是一種可以抵擋氧化壓力的催化物<ref name="pmid28076409" />。

=== 繁殖 ===
[[File:Flying_Termites_after_rain.jpg|替代=Hundreds of winged termite reproductives swarming after a summer rain, filling the field of the photograph.]]
有翅繁殖型只會在分飛時離開蟻巢。雌雄蟲會兩兩配對然後建立新的群體<ref name="v2010">{{cite web|title=Subterranean Termite Biology and Behavior|url=https://pubs.ext.vt.edu/444/444-502/444-502.html|accessdate=8 January 2015|date=5 March 2010|publisher=Virginia Tech (Virginia State University)|last1=Miller|first1=D.M.|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411182104/https://www.pubs.ext.vt.edu/444/444-502/444-502.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，蟻王蟻后只有在找到適合的地方築巢以後才會交配，它們會挖出一個腔室，關上入口然後交配<ref name="v2010" />，之後，蟻王蟻后永遠不會離開蟻巢。分飛時間因物種而異，有些物種在夏日白天分飛，有些在冬天白天分飛<ref name="Gouge">{{cite web|title=Drywood Termites|url=http://ag.arizona.edu/pubs/insects/az1232/|accessdate=16 September 2015|date=2001|work=Cooperative Extension, College of Agriculture & Life Sciences|publisher=University of Arizona|last1=Gouge|first1=D.H.|last2=Smith|first2=K.A.|last3=Olson|first3=C.|last4=Baker|first4=P.|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110102210/http://ag.arizona.edu/pubs/insects/az1232/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有在黃昏時分飛的物種，有翅型通常會被燈光吸引而大量聚集。分飛與否決定於環境因子，如時間、濕度、風速、降雨量<ref name="Gouge" />。群體中的個體數因物種而異，體型較大的物種個體數通常介於 100-1,000，有些物種個體數則可高達幾百萬隻<ref name="styria" />。

在新群體建立的一開始，蟻后只會產下 10-20 顆卵，但群體建立數年後的蟻后一天可產下 1,000 顆卵<ref name="aus" />。成熟群體的創始蟻后（primary queen） 的產卵能力很強，它的腹部會膨脹，且一天可產下 40,000 顆卵<ref>{{cite journal|title=Egg-laying in monogynous and polygynous colonies of the termite ''Macrotermes michaelseni'' (Isoptera, Macrotermitidae)|first1=M.|last2=Hacker|first2=M.|date=2001|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/PL00001771|volume=48|pages=231–237|last3=Brandl|first3=R.|last1=Kaib}}</ref>。一對成熟的卵巢各有大約 2,000 個卵巢管<ref>{{cite book|last1=Gilbert|first1=executive editors, G.A. Kerkut, L.I.|title=Comprehensive insect physiology, biochemistry, and pharmacology|date=1985|publisher=Pergamon Press|location=Oxford|isbn=978-0-08-026850-7|page=167|edition=1st|url=https://books.google.com/?id=bkTgBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA167&lpg=PA167&dq=termite+queen+ovarioles#v=onepage&q=termite%20queen%20ovarioles&f=false}}</ref>。膨大的腹部讓蟻后的體型大了好幾倍，導致蟻后失去移動能力，需要工蟻協助移動。

蟻王只會長大一點點，而且會一輩子持續的和蟻后交配（蟻后壽命可達30至50年），這點和螞蟻不同，螞蟻的蟻后只和雄蟻交配一次便能儲存能用上一輩子的精子，而雄蟻在交配完便會死去<ref name="Keller1998" /><ref name="Michael" />。如果蟻后死了，蟻王會製造能誘發新蟻后發育的費洛蒙<ref>{{cite book|last1=Wyatt|first1=T.D.|title=Pheromones and animal behaviour: communication by smell and taste|url=https://archive.org/details/pheromonesanimal0000wyat|url-access=registration|date=2003|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0-521-48526-5|page=[https://archive.org/details/pheromonesanimal0000wyat/page/119 119]|edition=Repr. with corrections 2004.}}</ref>。蟻王蟻后是一夫一妻制的，所以不會為了搶奪交配權競爭<ref>{{cite journal|title=How the sperm lost its tail: the evolution of aflagellate sperm.|first1=E.H.|date=2004|journal=Biological Reviews of the Cambridge Philosophical Society|issue=4|doi=10.1017/S1464793104006451|volume=79|pages=795–814|pmid=15682871|last1=Morrow}}</ref>。
[[File:Egg_grooming_behaviour_of_Reticulitermes_speratus_workers_in_a_nursery_cell_-_pone.0000813.s006.ogv|替代=In this movie, workers pick eggs from the egg pile, groom them and then return them into the egg pile. They coat the eggs with their saliva to protect them against drying out and to protect them against infection: the saliva contains lyzozyme which has antibacterial properties. The lysozyme also acts as an egg recognition pheromone.]]'' 工蟻正在對卵進行梳理行為（grooming）。]]
白蟻透過不完全變態來變成有翅型，而在有些物種中，有補充繁殖型的階級，它們會在蟻王或蟻后死亡或消失在群體中時發育成繁殖型<ref name="uflorida" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Supplementary reproductive|url=http://www2.hawaii.edu/~entomol/glossary/definition_supplementary_reproductive.htm|accessdate=16 September 2015|publisher=University of Hawaii|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030112432/http://www2.hawaii.edu/~entomol/glossary/definition_supplementary_reproductive.htm|archivedate=30 October 2014}}</ref>。補充繁殖型有能力取代死去的蟻王蟻后，且一個群體中可以有多個補充繁殖型<ref name="aus" />。有些物種蟻后可以行無性繁殖，研究顯示蟻后會和蟻王交配產下工蟻，但也會行無性繁殖產下自己的補充繁殖型（neotenics）<ref>{{cite journal|title=Termite queens close the sperm gates of eggs to switch from sexual to asexual reproduction|first1=T.|last2=Matsuura|first2=K.|date=2014|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=48|doi=10.1073/pnas.1412481111|volume=111|pages=17212–17217|bibcode=2014PNAS..11117212Y|pmc=4260566|pmid=25404335|last1=Yashiro}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Queen Succession Through Asexual Reproduction in Termites|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/73c1f923750e7fbffa869a34976647545775cf34|first1=K.|last2=Vargo|first2=E.L.|date=2009|journal=Science|issue=5922|doi=10.1126/science.1169702|volume=323|pages=1687|bibcode=2009Sci...323.1687M|pmid=19325106|last3=Kawatsu|first3=K.|last4=Labadie|first4=P. E.|last5=Nakano|first5=H.|last6=Yashiro|first6=T.|last7=Tsuji|first7=K.|last1=Matsuura}}</ref>。

在亞熱帶地區的白蟻 ''Embiratermes neotenicus'' 和其他近緣的物種中，一個群體包含一對創始蟻王蟻后和高達200隻補充繁殖型蟻后，這些補充繁殖型蟻后是透過雌性單性生殖產生<ref name="pmid26019158">{{cite journal|title=Asexual queen succession in the higher termite Embiratermes neotenicus|url=|date=June 2015|journal=Proc. Biol. Sci.|issue=1809|doi=10.1098/rspb.2015.0260|volume=282|pages=20150260|pmc=4590441|pmid=26019158|vauthors=Fougeyrollas R, Dolejšová K, Sillam-Dussès D, Roy V, Poteaux C, Hanus R, Roisin Y}}</ref>，這種方式可以確保配子異質性，從而避免近親繁殖導致基因衰敗。

== 行為和生態學 ==

=== 食性 ===
[[File:Termite_Fecal_Pellets.jpg|替代=A dense pile of termite faecal pellets, about 10 centimeters by 20 centimeters by several centimeters in height, which have accumulated on a wooden shelf from termite activity somewhere above the frame of this photograph.]]
白蟻為[[食碎屑动物|食碎屑者]]，於生態系中扮演重要的角色，負責分解死木、糞便或植物組織<ref>{{cite journal|title=The importance of termites (Isoptera) for the recycling of herbivore dung in tropical ecosystems: a review|first1=B.P.|last2=Buitenwerf|first2=R.|date=2008|journal=European Journal of Entomology|issue=2|doi=10.14411/eje.2008.025|volume=105|pages=165–173|last3=Desouza|first3=O.|last4=Olff|last1=Freymann}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Effects of habitat fragmentation on Amazonian termite communities|first1=O.F.|last2=Brown|first2=V.K.|date=2009|journal=Journal of Tropical Ecology|issue=2|doi=10.1017/S0266467400007847|volume=10|pages=197–206|last1=de Souza}}</ref>{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|pp=13–14}}。很多物種都取食纖維素，腸道特化可分解植物纖維<ref>{{cite journal|title=Cellulose digestion in the wood-eating higher termite, ''Nasutitermes takasagoensis'' (Shiraki): distribution of cellulases and properties of endo-beta-1,4-glucanase.|first1=G.|last2=Watanabe|first2=H.|date=1997|journal=Zoological Science|issue=1|doi=10.2108/zsj.14.83|volume=14|pages=83–93|pmid=9200983|last3=Matsumoto|first3=T.|last4=Noda|first4=H.|last1=Tokuda}}</ref>。白蟻被認為是大氣中甲烷的主要來源之一（11%），因其分解纖維素時會產生甲烷，甲烷是主要的溫室氣體之一<ref>{{cite book|last=Ritter|first=Michael|title=The Physical Environment: an Introduction to Physical Geography|url=http://www4.uwsp.edu/geo/faculty/ritter/geog101/textbook/atmosphere/atmospheric_composition_p2.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070518014844/http://www.uwsp.edu/geo/faculty/ritter/geog101/textbook/atmosphere/atmospheric_composition_p2.html|archivedate=18 May 2007|year=2006|publisher=University of Wisconsin|page=450}}</ref>。白蟻依賴腸道內的共生原生動物分解纖維素，白蟻會吸收纖維素被分解後的產物作為養分<ref>{{cite journal|title=Cospeciation of termite gut flagellates and their bacterial endosymbionts: ''Trichonympha'' species and ''Candidatus'' Endomicrobium trichonymphae|first1=W.|last2=Brune|first2=A.|date=2009|journal=Molecular Ecology|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1365-294X.2008.04029.x|volume=18|pages=332–342|pmid=19192183|last1=Ikeda-Ohtsubo}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Cellulose digestion in termites and cockroaches: What role do symbionts play?|first1=M.|date=1992|journal=Comparative Biochemistry and Physiology B|issue=4|doi=10.1016/0305-0491(92)90194-V|volume=103|pages=775–784|last1=Slaytor}}</ref>，而原生動物（如''Trichonympha''）則依賴附著於它們體表的共生細菌分泌消化酶。白蟻科可自行分泌纖維素酶，但它們仍然仰賴細菌分解大部分的纖維素，白蟻科沒有腸道共生原生動物<ref>{{cite journal|title=A cellulase gene of termite origin|first1=H..|last2=Noda|first2=H.|date=1998|journal=Nature|issue=6691|doi=10.1038/28527|volume=394|pages=330–331|bibcode=1998Natur.394..330W|pmid=9690469|last3=Tokuda|first3=G.|last4=Lo|first4=N.|last1=Watanabe}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hidden cellulases in termites: revision of an old hypothesis|first1=G.|last2=Watanabe|first2=H.|date=2007|journal=Biology Letters|issue=3|doi=10.1098/rsbl.2007.0073|volume=3|pages=336–339|pmc=2464699|pmid=17374589|last1=Tokuda}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Character of Cellulase Activity in the Guts of Flagellate-Free Termites with Different Feeding Habits|first1=Z.-Q.|last2=Liu|first2=B.-R.|date=2013|journal=Journal of Insect Science|issue=37|doi=10.1673/031.013.3701|volume=13|pages=37|pmc=3738099|pmid=23895662|last3=Zeng|first3=W.-H.|last4=Xiao|first4=W.-L.|last5=Li|first5=Q.-J.|last6=Zhong|first6=J.-H.|last1=Li}}</ref>。白蟻消化系統與腸道共生物的關係仍需更多研究。根據腸道內原生動物親緣關係，白蟻和隱尾蠊的原生動物可能是從共祖得來<ref>{{cite journal|title=The Cockroach origin of the termite gut microbiota: patterns in bacterial community structure reflect major evolutionary events|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_applied-and-environmental-microbiology_2014-04_80_7/page/2261|first1=C.|last2=Kohler|first2=T.|date=2014|journal=Applied and Environmental Microbiology|issue=7|doi=10.1128/AEM.04206-13|volume=80|pages=2261–2269|pmc=3993134|pmid=24487532|last3=Brune|first3=A.|last1=Dietrich}}</ref>。

某些物種食性會依季節改變，如 ''[[Gnathamitermes_tubiformans|Gnathamitermes tubiformans]]'' 夏天偏好取食 ''[[Aristida_longiseta|Aristida longiseta]]'' ，5月至8月偏好取食[[野牛草|野牛草]]，春天、夏天和秋天偏好取食[[格兰马草|格蘭馬草]]。''[[Gnathamitermes_tubiformans|Gnathamitermes tubiformans]]'' 秋天時比較活躍，因此所需要的食物量大於春天<ref>{{cite journal|title=Seasonal Food Habits of a Desert Termite, ''Gnathamitermes tubiformans'', in West Texas|first1=C.T.|last2=Foster|first2=D.E.|date=1980|journal=Environmental Entomology|issue=4|doi=10.1093/ee/9.4.461|volume=9|pages=461–466|last3=Ueckert|first3=D.N.|last1=Allen}}</ref>。

木頭的不同狀態會影響白蟻取食與否，相關因子包含濕度、材質、硬度、樹脂和木質素的含量。研究指出 ''Cryptotermes brevis'' 強烈偏好取食[[杨属|楊屬]]和[[枫属|楓屬]]的木材，而這兩屬的木材是大部分白蟻不吃的<ref>{{cite journal|title=Studies of Termite Wood-feeding Preferences|url=http://scholarspace.manoa.hawaii.edu/bitstream/handle/10125/10922/19_239-250.pdf?sequence=1|first1=E.A.|date=1966|journal=Hawaiian Entomological Society|issue=2|volume=19|pages=239–250|issn=0073-134X|last1=McMahan|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183151/https://scholarspace.manoa.hawaii.edu/bitstream/handle/10125/10922/19_239-250.pdf?sequence=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有些白蟻會種植真菌。白蟻會建造菌圃，種植 ''{{tsl|en|Termitomyces||Termitomyces}}'' 屬的真菌。當白蟻吃下孢子，孢子會完好的通過白蟻的腸道，最後隨著糞便離開白蟻體內，並在菌圃上成長<ref>{{cite journal|title=The evolution of fungus-growing termites and their mutualistic fungal symbionts|first1=D.K.|last2=Eggleton|first2=P.|date=2002|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=23|doi=10.1073/pnas.222313099|volume=99|pages=14887–14892|bibcode=2002PNAS...9914887A|jstor=3073687|pmc=137514|pmid=12386341|last3=Rouland-Lefevre|first3=C.|last4=Guldberg-Froslev|first4=T.|last5=Rosendahl|first5=S.|last6=Boomsma|first6=J.J.|last1=Aanen}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Fungus-farming insects: Multiple origins and diverse evolutionary histories|first1=U.G.|last2=Gerardo|first2=N.|date=2002|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=24|doi=10.1073/pnas.242594799|volume=99|pages=15247–15249|bibcode=2002PNAS...9915247M|pmc=137700|pmid=12438688|last1=Mueller}}</ref>。分子證據顯示[[大白蚁亚科|大白蟻亞科]]種植真菌的行為起源於3100萬年前。推測在非洲和亞洲半乾燥莽原（semiarid savannah） 中，9成的木材都由大白蟻亞科的物種分解。大白蟻亞科起源於雨林，種植真菌的行為使它們能夠擴殖非洲莽原，最終擴張到亞洲<ref name="Roberts_et_al_2016">{{cite journal|title=Oligocene termite nests with in situ fungus gardens from the Rukwa Rift Basin, Tanzania, support a paleogene African origin for insect agriculture|first1=E.M.|last2=Todd|first2=C.N.|date=2016|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=6|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0156847|volume=11|pages=e0156847|bibcode=2016PLoSO..1156847R|pmc=4917219|pmid=27333288|last3=Aanen|first3=D.K.|last4=Nobre|first4=T.|last5=Hilbert-Wolf|first5=H.L.|last6=O'Connor|first6=P.M.|last7=Tapanila|first7=L.|last8=Mtelela|first8=C.|last9=Stevens|first9=N.J.|last1=Roberts}}</ref>。

白蟻可根據食性粗分為兩大類：高等白蟻和低等白蟻。低等白蟻主要取食木材，由於一般的木材難以消化，白蟻偏好於取食受真菌感染的木材，真菌感染的木材較容易消化，且真菌富含蛋白。高等白蟻食性多樣，取食糞便、腐植質、草、落葉和根<ref>{{cite journal|title=Flagellates, bacteria, and fungi associated with termites: diversity and function in nutrition – a review|url=http://large.stanford.edu/publications/coal/references/docs/radek.pdf|first1=R.|date=1999|journal=Ecotropica|volume=5|pages=183–196|last1=Radek|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183154/http://large.stanford.edu/publications/coal/references/docs/radek.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。低等白蟻腸道內含有很多種細菌和原生動物，而高等白蟻只有少數幾種細菌且無原生動物<ref>{{cite journal|title=Role of microorganisms in the digestion of lignocellulose by termites|first1=J.A.|last2=Brune|first2=A.|date=1993|journal=Annual Review of Entomology|issue=1|doi=10.1146/annurev.en.39.010194.002321|volume=39|pages=453–487|last1=Breznak}}</ref>。

=== 共生 ===
高等白蟻 （higher termites） 是指白蟻科，其他非白蟻科的白蟻稱為低等白蟻 （lower termites）。高低等白蟻一個主要的差異在於高等白蟻的腸道內沒有共生原生動物。

==== 體內共生 ====
白蟻依靠後腸內的生物來協助他們分解纖維素，低等白蟻主要依靠原生動物，高等白蟻腸內則沒有原生動物，它們靠細菌來協助他們分解纖維素。白蟻腸道內的原生動物共有兩門，分別為[[副基體綱|副基體綱]]和[[前軸柱綱|前軸柱綱]] (Preaxostyla) ，其中前軸柱綱的原生動物皆屬於[[銳滴蟲目|銳滴蟲目]] (Oxymonadida)<ref>{{Cite book|title=Archibald|first=Čepička I., Dolan M.F., Gile G.H.|publisher=Springer, Cham|year=2016|isbn=978-3-319-32669-6|location=|pages=|chapter=Parabasalia}}</ref>。

==== 體外共生 ====
[[白蟻科|白蟻科]]中的[[大白蟻亞科|大白蟻亞科]]會蓋菌圃，並種植真菌，取食孢子。[[台灣土白蟻|台灣土白蟻]] （''Coptotermes'' ''formosanus'' ） 與[[雞肉絲菇|雞肉絲菇]] （''Termitomyces'' ''eurhizus'' ） 共生，雞肉絲菇的孢子中含有[[色胺酸|色胺酸]]（tryptophan），色胺酸為必需胺基酸，台灣土白蟻無法自行合成色胺酸，只能藉由攝食雞肉絲菇的孢子取得<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Fungal nutrition allocation enhances mutualism with fungus-growing termite|author=Chun-I Chiu, Jie-Hao Ou, Chi-Yu Chen & Hou-Feng Li|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S1754504818303994|journal=Fungal Ecology|issue=41|doi=10.1016/j.funeco.2019.04.001|others=|year=2019|volume=|page=92-100|pmid=|access-date=2020-03-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183159/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S1754504818303994|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 天敵 ===
[[File:Crab_Spider_(Thomisidae)_and_Winged_Termite_prey_(12640038823).jpg|缩略图]]捕食白蟻有翅型]]
白蟻有很多天敵，曾有研究指出 65 種鳥類和 19 種哺乳類會取食 ''{{tsl|en|Hodotermes||Hodotermes mossambicus}}'' <ref>{{cite journal|title=Bird and mammal predators of the harvester termite ''Hodotermes mossambicus'' (Hagen) in semi-arid regions of South Africa|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_south-african-journal-of-science_1990-01_86_1/page/34|first1=O.B.|last2=Hewitt|first2=P.H.|date=1990|journal=South African Journal of Science|issue=1|volume=86|pages=34–37|issn=0038-2353|last1=Kok}}</ref>。螞蟻<ref name="HW1990">{{cite book|last1=Hölldobler|first1=B.|last2=Wilson|first2=E.O.|title=The Ants|date=1990|publisher=Belknap Press of Harvard University Press|pages=[https://archive.org/details/ants0000hlld/page/559 559–566]|location=Cambridge, Massachusetts|isbn=978-0-674-04075-5|title-link=The Ants}}</ref><ref name="ant_fight_termite">{{cite journal|title=Prospects for the biological control of subterranean termites (Isoptera: Rhinotermitidae), with special reference to ''Coptotermes formosanus''|first1=T.W.|last2=Grace|first2=J.K.|date=2000|journal=Bulletin of Entomological Research|issue=1|doi=10.1017/S0007485300000663|volume=90|pages=9–21|pmid=10948359|last1=Culliney}}</ref>、蜈蚣、蟑螂、蟋蟀、蜻蜓、蠍子、蜘蛛<ref>{{cite journal|title=Plant and invertebrate assemblages on old fields in the arid southern Karoo, South Africa|first1=W.R.J.|last2=Milton|first2=S.J.|date=1995|journal=African Journal of Ecology|issue=1|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2028.1995.tb00777.x|volume=33|pages=1–13|last1=Dean}}</ref>、蜥蜴<ref>{{cite book|last1=Wade|first1=W.W.|title=Ecology of Desert Systems|date=2002|publisher=Elsevier|location=Burlington|isbn=978-0-08-050499-5|page=216}}</ref>、青蛙<ref>{{cite book|last1=Reagan|first1=D.P.|last2=Waide|first2=R.B.|title=The food web of a tropical rain forest|date=1996|publisher=University of Chicago Press|location=Chicago|isbn=978-0-226-70599-6|page=[https://archive.org/details/foodweboftropica0000unse/page/294 294]|url=https://archive.org/details/foodweboftropica0000unse/page/294}}</ref>都會吃白蟻，有兩種 {{tsl|en|Ammoxenidae||Ammoxenidae}} 科的蜘蛛專食白蟻<ref name="Services2013">{{cite book|last1=Bardgett|first1=R.D.|last2=Herrick|first2=J.E.|last3=Six|first3=J.|last4=Jones|first4=T.H.|last5=Strong|first5=D.R.|last6=van der Putten|first6=W.H.|title=Soil ecology and ecosystem services|date=2013|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=978-0-19-968816-6|page=178|edition=1st}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Choe|first1=J.C.|last2=Crespi|first2=B.J.|title=The evolution of social behavior in insects and arachnids|url=https://archive.org/details/evolutionsocialb00choe|date=1997|publisher=Cambridge university press|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0-521-58977-2|page=[https://archive.org/details/evolutionsocialb00choe/page/76 76]|edition=1st}}</ref>{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=509}}。土豚、土狼、食蟻獸、蝙蝠、熊、兔耳袋狸、許多鳥類、針鼴、狐狸、嬰猴、袋食蟻獸、老鼠和穿山甲也會取食白蟻<ref name="Services2013" /><ref name="wilson2014">{{cite book|last1=Abe|first1=Y.|last2=Bignell|first2=D.E.|last3=Higashi|first3=T.|title=Termites: Evolution, Sociality, Symbioses, Ecology|date=2014|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-94-017-3223-9|doi=10.1007/978-94-017-3223-9|pages=124–149}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Above ground defence in the harvester termite, ''Hodotermes mossambicus''|first1=D.S.|last2=Clark|first2=A.B.|date=1977|journal=Journal of the Entomological Society of South Africa|volume=40|pages=271–282|last1=Wilson}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Lavelle|first1=P.|last2=Spain|first2=A.V.|title=Soil ecology|url=https://archive.org/details/soilecology00lave|date=2001|publisher=Kluwer Academic|location=Dordrecht|isbn=978-0-306-48162-8|edition=2nd|page=[https://archive.org/details/soilecology00lave/page/n340 316]}}</ref>。

[[土狼|土狼]]是一種專食昆蟲的哺乳類，主食為白蟻。土狼透過聲音尋找獵物，也會透過白蟻兵蟻釋放的味道尋找白蟻。一隻土狼用長又黏的舌頭取食白蟻，一個晚上可以吃掉上千隻白蟻<ref>{{cite encyclopedia|last1=Richardson|first1=P.K.R.|last2=Bearder|first2=S.K.|editor1-last=MacDonald|editor1-first=D.|encyclopedia=The Encyclopedia of Mammals|title=The Hyena Family|isbn=978-0-87196-871-5|publisher=Facts on File Publication|location=New York, NY|year=1984|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma00mals_0/page/158 158–159]|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofma00mals_0/page/158}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Mills|first1=G.|last2=Harvey|first2=M.|title=African Predators|url=https://archive.org/details/africanpredators0000mill_d0p3|publisher=Smithsonian Institution Press|location=Washington, D.C.|year=2001|isbn=978-1-56098-096-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/africanpredators0000mill_d0p3/page/71 71]}}</ref>。懶熊會用爪破壞蟻丘，而黑猩猩則會使用工具把白蟻「釣」出蟻巢。根據骨制工具上的使用痕跡，學者認為[[羅百氏傍人|羅百氏傍人]]會用工具破壞蟻丘<ref>{{cite journal|title=Assessing the function of early hominin bone tools|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/229364355|first1=F.|last2=Backwell|first2=L.|date=2009|journal=Journal of Archaeological Science|issue=8|doi=10.1016/j.jas.2009.04.005|volume=36|pages=1764–1773|last1=d'Errico}}</ref>。

[[File:Megaponera_analis_major_killing_macrotermes_soldier.jpg|左]] (''Megaponera analis'') 正在攻擊[[兇猛大白蟻|兇猛大白蟻]] (''Macrotermes bellicosus'') 。]]
螞蟻是白蟻最主要的天敵<ref name="HW1990" /><ref name="ant_fight_termite" />，有些種類的螞蟻專食白蟻，如 ''[[Megaponera|Megaponera]]'' 屬，''[[Megaponera|Megaponera]]'' 屬只吃白蟻，它們會行軍捕食白蟻，行軍時間可維持數小時<ref name="lepage">{{cite journal|title=Étude de la prédation de ''Megaponera foetens'' (F.) sur les populations récoltantes de Macrotermitinae dans un ecosystème semi-aride (Kajiado-Kenya)|first1=M.G.|date=1981|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/BF02223627|volume=28|pages=247–262|language=es|last1=Lepage}}</ref><ref name="Levieux1966">{{cite journal|title=Note préliminaire sur les colonnes de chasse de ''Megaponera fœtens'' F. (Hyménoptère Formicidæ)|first1=J.|date=1966|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=2|doi=10.1007/BF02223567|volume=13|pages=117–126|language=fr|last1=Levieux}}</ref>；''{{tsl|en|Paltothyreus||Paltothyreus tarsatus}}'' 也會行軍捕食白蟻，它們會用大顎抓住盡可能多的白蟻帶回家，在行軍途中它們會沿途留下化學訊息，其他個體會沿著化學訊息加入行軍<ref name="HW1990" />；''{{tsl|en|Eurhopalothrix||Eurhopalothrix heliscata}}'' 則會從朽木的縫隙進入，獵捕居住在朽木中的白蟻<ref name="HW1990" />；''{{tsl|en|Tetramorium||Tetramorium uelense}}'' 則獵食小型白蟻，在外覓食的工蟻偵查到白蟻後會帶來10到30隻的工蟻一起獵捕，它們會用螫針使白蟻失去行動能力<ref>{{cite journal|title=Chemical crypsis in predatory ants|first1=C.|last2=Baker|first2=R.|date=1979|journal=Experientia|issue=7|doi=10.1007/BF01955119|volume=35|pages=870–872|last3=Howse|first3=P.E.|last1=Longhurst}}</ref>；''{{tsl|en|Centromyrmex||Centromyrmex}}'' 和[[虹琉璃蟻屬|虹琉璃蟻屬]]有時候會在蟻丘內築巢並取食白蟻，但除了獵食以外，白蟻和這兩屬的螞蟻並沒有其他交互關係<ref name="wheeler1936">{{cite journal|title=Ecological relations of Ponerine and other ants to termites|url=https://zenodo.org/record/25265|first1=W.M.|date=1936|journal=Proceedings of the American Academy of Arts and Sciences|issue=3|doi=10.2307/20023221|volume=71|pages=159–171|jstor=20023221|last1=Wheeler|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183219/https://zenodo.org/record/25265|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Shattuck">{{cite journal|title=Revision of the ant genus ''Iridomyrmex'' (Hymenoptera : Formicidae)|url=http://www.antwiki.org/wiki/images/a/ab/Heterick_%26_Shattuck.pdf|first1=S.O.|last2=Heterick|first2=B.E.|date=2011|journal=Zootaxa|volume=2845|pages=1–74|isbn=978-1-86977-676-3|issn=1175-5334|last1=Shattuck|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145707/https://www.antwiki.org/wiki/images/a/ab/Heterick_%26_Shattuck.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>；其他螞蟻如''{{tsl|en|Acanthostichus||Acanthostichus}}'' 、[[巨山蟻屬|巨山蟻屬]]、舉尾家蟻屬（''Crematogaster'' ）、''{{tsl|en|Cylindromyrmex||Cylindromyrmex}}、''細顎針蟻屬（''{{tsl|en|Leptogenys||Leptogenys}}'' ）、[[鋸針蟻|鋸針蟻屬]]、''{{tsl|en|Ophthalmopone||Ophthalmopone}}''、''{{tsl|en|Pachycondyla||Pachycondyla}}''、''{{tsl|en|Rhytidoponera||Rhytidoponera}}''、[[火蟻屬|火家蟻屬]]、''{{tsl|en|Wasmannia||Wasmannia}}'' 也會取食白蟻<ref name="HW1990" /><ref name="wilson2014" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Enemy deterrence in the recruitment strategy of a termite: Soldier-organized foraging in ''Nasutitermes costalis''|first1=J.F.A.|date=1981|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=3|doi=10.1073/pnas.78.3.1976|volume=78|pages=1976–1979|bibcode=1981PNAS...78.1976T|pmc=319259|pmid=16592995|last1=Traniello}}</ref>。[[矛蚁属|矛蟻屬]]則很少會取食白蟻，儘管矛蟻屬的食性極廣<ref>{{cite journal|title=Driver Ants Invading a Termite Nest: why do the most catholic predators of all seldom take this abundant prey?|url=http://www.doctorbugs.com/dorylus.pdf|first1=C.|last2=Moffett|first2=M.W.|date=2007|journal=Biotropica|issue=5|doi=10.1111/j.1744-7429.2007.00296.x|volume=39|pages=663–667|last1=Schöning|author=|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112035412/http://www.doctorbugs.com/Dorylus.pdf|archive-date=2015-11-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

螞蟻並非唯一會行軍的無脊椎動物，很多[[狩蜂類|狩蜂類]]、''{{tsl|en|Polybia||Polybia Lepeletier}}'' 、''{{tsl|en|Angiopolybia pallens||Angiopolybia Araujo}}'' 、也會在白蟻分飛時攻擊蟻丘<ref>{{cite journal|title=Observations on Brazilian termite alate swarms and some structures used in the dispersal of reproductives (Isoptera: Termitidae)|first1=A.E.|date=1983|journal=Journal of Natural History|issue=3|doi=10.1080/00222938300770231|volume=17|pages=309–320|last1=Mill}}</ref>。

=== 寄生蟲、病原體和病毒 ===
比起蜂類和螞蟻，白蟻比較不會被寄生蟲攻擊，因為它們通常躲在蟻巢中被保護得好好的{{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|p=61}}{{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|p=75}}，然而，白蟻還是會被一些寄生蟲攻擊，如有些雙翅目蠅類、''Pyemotes'' 屬的蟎、和很多種線蟲，這些線蟲大部分為[[小桿目|小桿目]]的物種{{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|p=59}}，還有 ''[[Mermis|Mermis]]'' 屬、''[[Diplogaster_aerivora|Diplogaster aerivora]] 、{{tsl|en|Heterakis gallinarum||Harteria gallinarum}}'' {{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|pp=301–302}}。群體可能會透過遷徙來躲避寄生蟲{{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|p=19}}。

真菌病原體 ''{{tsl|en|Aspergillus nomius||Aspergillus nomius}}'' 和[[黑殭菌|黑僵菌]]會威脅蟻群，因為這兩種真菌並沒有寄主專一性，且可以感染巢中大量的個體<ref>{{cite journal|title=Pyemotes – mites as parasites of termites|first1=J.|last2=Hrdy|first2=I.|date=2009|journal=Zeitschrift für Angewandte Entomologie|issue=1–4|doi=10.1111/j.1439-0418.1962.tb04062.x|volume=51|pages=94–97|last1=Weiser}}</ref><ref name="resource">{{cite journal|title=Resource competition between two fungal parasites in subterranean termites.|first1=T.|last2=Efstathion|first2=C.A.|date=2012|journal=Die Naturwissenschaften|issue=11|doi=10.1007/s00114-012-0977-2|volume=99|pages=949–58|bibcode=2012NW.....99..949C|pmid=23086391|last3=Elliott|first3=M.L.|last4=Su|first4=N.Y.|last1=Chouvenc}}</ref>。真菌透過接觸傳染{{sfn|Schmid-Hempel|1998|pp=38, 102}}。 ''M. anisopliae'' 會削弱白蟻的免疫能力。''A. nomius'' 只有在群體受到極大壓力時才能感染個體。

可能感染白蟻的病毒包括 {{tsl|en|Entomopoxvirinae||Entomopoxvirinae}} 和核多角病毒<ref>{{cite journal|title=Virus-like symptoms in a termite (Isoptera: Kalotermitidae) field colony|first1=T.|last2=Mullins|first2=A.J.|date=2013|journal=Florida Entomologist|issue=4|doi=10.1653/024.096.0450|volume=96|pages=1612–1614|last3=Efstathion|first3=C.A.|last4=Su|first4=N.-Y.|last1=Chouvenc}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Infection of Termites by ''Spodoptera littoralis'' Nuclear Polyhedrosis Virus|first1=A.A.|last2=Hassan|first2=F.A.|date=2011|journal=International Journal of Tropical Insect Science|issue=1|doi=10.1017/S1742758400009991|volume=9|pages=37–39|last1=Al Fazairy}}</ref>（{{tsl|en|Nuclear Polyhedrosis Virus||Nuclear Polyhedrosis Virus}}）。

=== 移動方式和覓食 ===
工蟻和兵蟻沒有翅膀，而有翅型在分飛後就會把翅膀剝落，因此白蟻主要的移動方式還是靠行走{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=11}}。

白蟻覓食的方式因種類而異，巢食共處型的會取食它們所居住的木頭，而巢食連接型和巢食分離型會出巢覓食<ref>{{cite book|last1=Traniello|first1=J.F.A.|last2=Leuthold|first2=R.H.|title=Behavior and Ecology of Foraging in Termites|date=2000|pages=141–168|doi=10.1007/978-94-017-3223-9_7|isbn=978-94-017-3223-9|publisher=Springer Netherlands}}</ref>。大部分的工蟻不會在外活動，也不會在沒有遮蔽物的環境下覓食，它們會沿路建築蟻道，藉此保護自身{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=13}}。鼻白蟻科會建築蟻道來尋找食物，而找到食物的工蟻會留下費洛蒙，藉此吸引更多同伴前來取食<ref>{{cite journal|title=Trail communication during foraging and recruitment in the subterranean termite ''Reticulitermes santonensis'' De Feytaud (Isoptera, Rhinotermitidae)|first1=J.|last2=Kaib|first2=M.|date=2001|journal=Journal of Insect Behavior|issue=2|doi=10.1023/A:1007881510237|volume=14|pages=157–171|last1=Reinhard}}</ref>。覓食的工蟻會沿路留下訊息費洛蒙，訊息費洛蒙由腹板腺分泌<ref name="commu">{{cite book|last1=Costa-Leonardo|first1=A.M.|last2=Haifig|first2=I.|title=''Termite communication during different behavioral activities'' in Biocommunication of Animals|date=2013|pages=161–190|doi=10.1007/978-94-007-7414-8_10|publisher=Springer Netherlands|isbn=978-94-007-7413-1}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Morphology of the sternal gland in workers of ''Coptotermes gestroi'' (Isoptera, Rhinotermitidae).|first1=A.M.|date=2006|journal=Micron|issue=6|doi=10.1016/j.micron.2005.12.006|volume=37|pages=551–556|pmid=16458523|last1=Costa-Leonardo}}</ref>。 ''[[Nasutitermes_costalis|Nasutitermes costalis]]'' 的覓食行為可分成三個階段，第一階段兵蟻會出外覓食，當它們找到食物時，它們會釋放訊息，接收到訊息後其他兵蟻和一小群工蟻會前往食物所在地；第二階段，食物所在地會出現大量的工蟻；第三階段，兵蟻的數量減少，工蟻的數量增加<ref>{{cite journal|title=Chemical regulation of polyethism during foraging in the neotropical termite ''Nasutitermes costalis''|first1=J.F.|last2=Busher|first2=C.|date=1985|journal=Journal of Chemical Ecology|issue=3|doi=10.1007/BF01411418|volume=11|pages=319–32|pmid=24309963|last1=Traniello}}</ref>。

工蟻會隨機行走（{{tsl|en|Lévy flight||Lévy flight}}） 來尋找同伴或食物<ref>{{cite journal|title=Lévy flights and self-similar exploratory behaviour of termite workers: beyond model fitting|first1=O.|last2=DeSouza|first2=O.|date=2014|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=10|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0111183|volume=9|pages=e111183|arxiv=1410.0930|bibcode=2014PLoSO...9k1183M|pmc=4213025|pmid=25353958|last3=Paiva|first3=L.R.|last4=Marins|first4=A.|last5=Orozco|first5=S.|last6=Aegerter|first6=C.M.|last1=Miramontes}}</ref>。

=== 競爭 ===
兩群體間的競爭往往是透過儀式性打鬥（{{tsl|en|agonistic behaviour||agonistic behaviour}}） 進行，競爭會導致個體死亡，和領地的得失<ref>{{cite journal|title=A comparative tunnelling network approach to assess interspecific competition effects in termites|first1=C.|last2=Haifig|first2=I.|date=2012|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s00040-012-0229-7|volume=59|pages=369–379|last3=de Camargo-Dietrich|first3=C.R.R.|last4=Costa-Leonardo|first4=A.M.|last1=Jost}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Intra- and interspecific agonism in ''Reticulitermes flavipes'' (Kollar) and ''R. virginicus'' (Banks) and effects of arena and group size in laboratory assays|first1=J.M.|last2=Forschler|first2=B.T.|date=1998|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s000400050067|volume=45|pages=43–49|last1=Polizzi}}</ref>。打鬥中死去的個體可能會被集中埋起來<ref>{{cite journal|title=The underground passages and storage pits used in foraging by a nest of the termite ''Macrotermes michaelseni'' in Kajiado, Kenya|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_canadian-journal-of-zoology_1982-02_60_2/page/237|first1=J.P.E.C.|date=1982|journal=Journal of Zoology|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1469-7998.1982.tb02073.x|volume=198|pages=237–247|last1=Darlington}}</ref>。

研究顯示當屬於不同群體的白蟻相遇時，有些個體會故意擋住另一方的去路，以阻止它回巢留下費洛蒙訊息，讓更多工蟻前來支援<ref name="commu" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Effect of soil type and moisture availability on the foraging behavior of the Formosan subterranean termite (Isoptera: Rhinotermitidae).|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-entomology_2010-06_103_3/page/799|first1=M.L.|last2=Osbrink|first2=W.L.|date=2010|journal=Journal of Economic Entomology|issue=3|doi=10.1603/EC09250|volume=103|pages=799–807|pmid=20568626|last1=Cornelius}}</ref>。如果陌生群體的屍體堵在探索用的隧道中，白蟻會選擇另闢新路而不是移開屍體<ref>{{cite journal|title=Subterranean termites (Isoptera: Rhinotermitidae): Exploitation of equivalent food resources with different forms of placement|first1=J.|last2=Costa-Leonardo|first2=A.M.|date=2012|journal=Insect Science|issue=3|doi=10.1111/j.1744-7917.2011.01453.x|volume=19|pages=412–418|last1=Toledo Lima}}</ref>。兩個群體相遇時不總是會打鬥，雖然它們可能會擋住對方的去路，但是不一定會打鬥，如 ''Macrotermes bellicosus'' 和 ''Macrotermes subhyalinus'' 就是如此''<ref>{{cite journal|title=Intraspecific colony recognition in the termites ''Macrotermes subhyalinus'' and ''Macrotermes bellicosus'' (Isoptera, Termitidae)|first1=P.|last2=Leuthold|first2=R.H.|date=1999|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s000400050128|volume=46|pages=164–170|last1=Jmhasly}}</ref>''。有些白蟻會自殺式的堵住道路，以防止敵人入侵，如台灣家白蟻，它們會擠進隧道裡面然後死在那邊，以堵塞通道進而阻止後續的打鬥<ref>{{cite journal|title=Agonistic behavior between colonies of the Formosan subterranean termite (Isoptera: Rhinotermitidae) from Louis Armstrong Park, New Orleans, Louisiana|first1=M.T.|last2=Su|first2=N.Y.|date=2005|journal=Sociobiology|issue=2|volume=45|pages=331–345|last1=Messenger}}</ref>。

在繁殖階級中，補充繁殖型的雌蟲可能會互相競爭，以搶奪繁殖地位，最後會剩下一隻蟻后存活<ref>{{cite journal|title=A gene necessary for reproductive suppression in termites|url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/17774174a69833e904f68e1828306e0ae475336a|first1=J.|last2=Weil|first2=T.|date=2009|journal=Science|issue=5928|doi=10.1126/science.1170660|volume=324|pages=758|bibcode=2009Sci...324..758K|pmid=19423819|last3=Hoffmann|first3=K.|last4=Foster|first4=K.R.|last5=Rehli|first5=M.|last1=Korb}}</ref>。

螞蟻和白蟻可能會互相競爭築巢地點，特別是具有補食白蟻習性的螞蟻，它們通常會對樹棲型白蟻產生不良影響<ref name="arb">{{cite journal|title=Predation and interference competition between ants (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) and arboreal termites (Isoptera: Termitidae)|url=http://www.repositorio.ufop.br/bitstream/123456789/4835/1/ARTIGO_PredationInterferenceCompetition.pdf|first1=T.T.G.|last2=Reis|first2=R.|date=2005|journal=Sociobiology|issue=2|volume=46|pages=409–419|last3=DeSouza|first3=O.|last4=Ribeiro|first4=S.P.|last1=Mathew|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411182243/https://www.repositorio.ufop.br/bitstream/123456789/4835/1/ARTIGO_PredationInterferenceCompetition.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 溝通 ===
[[File:Termites_(Nasutitermes_sp.)_(8439859723).jpg|缩略图]]
大部分白蟻沒有視覺，主要依靠化學分子、觸覺和費洛蒙溝通，溝通內容包含覓食、尋找繁殖蟻、建築蟻巢、分辨同伴、分飛、尋找並攻擊敵人、抵禦巢穴<ref name="Leonardo2">{{cite journal|title=Pheromones and exocrine glands in Isoptera|first1=A.M.|last2=Haifig|first2=I.|date=2010|journal=Vitamins and Hormones|doi=10.1016/S0083-6729(10)83021-3|volume=83|pages=521–549|isbn=9780123815163|pmid=20831960|last1=Costa-Leonardo}}</ref><ref name="commu" />。最頻繁的溝通方式是透過觸角<ref name="commu" />。已發現的費洛蒙有接觸費洛蒙（contact pheromones）（透過交哺和清理同伴身體傳播）、警戒費洛蒙、標跡費洛蒙、性費洛蒙等。警戒費洛蒙和防禦性化學物質由前額腺分泌；標跡費洛蒙由腹板腺分泌；性費洛蒙由腹板腺和背板腺分泌<ref name="Leonardo2" />。白蟻出外覓食時會排成一列。蟻道會包覆其他物體，蟻道成分為糞便，工蟻會在蟻道中留下費洛蒙，其他個體會透過味覺受器感知費洛蒙<ref name="Britannica2">{{cite encyclopedia|last1=Krishna|first1=K.|title=Termite|url=http://www.britannica.com/animal/termite|encyclopedia=Encyclopædia Britannica|accessdate=11 September 2015|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421121202/https://www.britannica.com/animal/termite|dead-url=no}}</ref>。白蟻可以透過化學訊息、震動和肢體接觸來溝通<ref name="Britannica2" /><ref name="commu" />。

白蟻築巢時使用的是間接構通。白蟻築巢的行為是出自於個體本身的，而並非由某些個體負責發號施令。白蟻放下建材時會刺激其他白蟻放下更多建材，因此白蟻建築與否是取決於環境，而非取決於與同伴構通的結果<ref name="commu" />。

白蟻透過表皮碳氫化合物來分辨同伴<ref>{{cite journal|title=Chemical communication in isoptera|first1=A.M.|last2=Casarin|first2=F.E.|date=2009|journal=Neotropical Entomology|issue=1|doi=10.1590/S1519-566X2009000100001|volume=38|pages=747–52|pmid=19347093|last3=Lima|first3=J.T.|last1=Costa-Leonardo}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Intracolony chemical communication in social insects|url=http://www4.ncsu.edu/~jhhunt/Richard%20and%20Hunt.pdf|first1=F.-J.|last2=Hunt|first2=J.H.|date=2013|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s00040-013-0306-6|volume=60|pages=275–291|last1=Richard|author=|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114501/http://www4.ncsu.edu/~jhhunt/Richard%20and%20Hunt.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Cuticular hydrocarbon composition reflects genetic relationship among colonies of the introduced termite ''Reticulitermes santonensis'' Feytaud|first1=S.|last2=Lohou|first2=C.|date=2006|journal=Journal of Chemical Ecology|issue=5|doi=10.1007/s10886-006-9043-x|volume=32|pages=1027–1042|pmid=16739021|last3=Christides|first3=J.P.|last4=Bagnères|first4=A.G.|last1=Dronnet}}</ref>。

=== 防禦 ===
[[File:Termites_rush_to_damaged_portion_of_mound.jpg|替代=To demonstrate termite repair behaviour, a hole was bored into a termite nest. Over a dozen worker termites with pale heads are visible in this close-up photo, most facing the camera as they engage in repair activities from the inside of the hole. About a dozen soldier termites with orange heads are also visible, some facing outwards from the hole, others patrolling the surrounding area.]]
蟻巢被破壞或被入侵時白蟻會釋放警戒費洛蒙，兵蟻會前往警戒費洛蒙的位置禦敵<ref name="commu" />。白蟻警戒時會持續抽動，發出震動，有些種類兵蟻受侵擾時會從前額腺釋放液體並排出含有警戒費洛蒙的糞便<ref name="commu" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Above ground predator defense in the harvester termite, ''Hodotermes mossambicus'' (Hagen)|first1=D.S.|date=1977|journal=Journal of the Entomological Society of Southern Africa|volume=40|pages=271–282|last1=Wilson}}</ref>。

被[[黑殭菌|黑僵菌]]感染的個體會震動發出訊號，其他個體接收到訊號後會避開受感染的個體<ref name="rosengaus1999">{{cite journal|title=Immunity in a social insect|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_naturwissenschaften_1999-12_86_12/page/588|first1=R.B.|last2=Traniello|first2=J.F.A.|date=1999|journal=Naturwissenschaften|issue=12|doi=10.1007/s001140050679|volume=86|pages=588–591|bibcode=1999NW.....86..588R|last3=Chen|first3=T.|last4=Brown|first4=J.J.|last5=Karp|first5=R.D.|last1=Rosengaus}}</ref>。如果黑僵菌感染的狀況極為嚴重，整個群體可能會因此滅亡，但發生這種狀況的機率極低<ref name="wilson">{{cite book|last1=Wilson|first1=E.O.|authorlink=E. O. Wilson|title=A window on eternity: a biologist's walk through Gorongosa National Park|url=https://archive.org/details/windowoneternity0000wils|date=2014|publisher=Simon & Schuster|isbn=978-1-4767-4741-5|pages=[https://archive.org/details/windowoneternity0000wils/page/85 85], 90|edition=First}}</ref>。

有些物種的兵蟻頭部前方呈截面狀，受侵擾時會用頭部塞住出入口，藉此禦敵<ref>{{cite book|last1=Belbin|first1=R.M.|title=The Coming Shape of Organization|date=2013|publisher=Routledge|location=New York|isbn=978-1-136-01553-3|page=27}}</ref>，如截頭堆沙白蟻（''Cryptotermes'' ''domesticus'' ）。如果出入口大於兵蟻的頭部，數隻兵蟻會一起擋在出入口並嘗試鉗咬入侵者<ref name="wilson" />。

蟻道受破壞時會觸發警戒，儘管破壞程度極低。警戒時兵蟻會聚集在破壞處，並釋放警戒費洛蒙吸引更多兵蟻前來，也吸引工蟻前來修補破口<ref name="Britannica2" />。警戒的白蟻會顯得躁動，當它撞到另一個個體時也會讓另一個體警戒，並留下警戒費洛蒙，白蟻藉此來加強警戒並招募更多個體協防破口<ref name="Britannica2" />。

泛熱帶地區的象白蟻亞科兵蟻高度特化，前額腺外突，形成象鼻狀的管狀結構，可透過釋放化學物質來防禦<ref name=":2">{{cite journal|title=Soldier defense secretions of ''Trinervitermes bettonianus'' (Isoptera, Nasutitermitinae): Chemical variation in allopatric populations|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-ecology_1981-01_7_1/page/147|first1=G.D.|last2=Chen|first2=D.|date=1981|journal=Journal of Chemical Ecology|issue=1|doi=10.1007/BF00988642|volume=7|pages=147–157|pmid=24420434|last1=Prestwich}}</ref>。象鼻兵蟻大顎退化，無法自行取食，需透過工蟻餵食<ref name="biosyn2">{{cite journal|title=From tetracycles to macrocycles|first1=G.D.|date=1982|journal=Tetrahedron|issue=13|doi=10.1016/0040-4020(82)80040-9|volume=38|pages=1911–1919|last1=Prestwich}}</ref>。象白蟻亞科分泌的液體中含有多種單萜烯類<ref name=":2" />。同樣也具有從前額腺分泌液體的還有[[鼻白蟻科|鼻白蟻科]]的臺灣家白蟻（''Coptotermes'' ''formosanus'' ），臺灣家白蟻分泌的液體中還有萘<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Termites fumigate their nests with naphthalene|last=Chen|first=J.|last2=Henderson|first2=G.|date=1998-04-09|journal=Nature|issue=6676|doi=10.1038/33305|volume=392|pages=558–559|bibcode=1998Natur.392..558C|last3=Grimm|first3=C. C.|last4=Lloyd|first4=S. W.|last5=Laine|first5=R. A.}}</ref>。
[[File:Nasute_termite_soldiers.png|左]]
''{{tsl|en|Globitermes sulphureus||Globitermes sulphureus}}'' 的兵蟻會透過自爆來防禦，它們會擠破表皮底下的腺體，並放出濃稠的黃色液體，液體接觸空氣後會變得非常黏稠，可以困住入侵的螞蟻或其他昆蟲<ref name="Extraordinary_Animals">{{citation|title=Extraordinary Animals: An Encyclopedia of Curious and Unusual Animals|first=Ross|last=Piper|year=2007|page=26|isbn=978-0-313-33922-6|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eqegRf2UstIC&q=termite#v=snippet&q=termite&f=false|publisher=Greenwood Press|accessdate=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183235/https://books.google.com/books?id=eqegRf2UstIC&q=termite#v=snippet&q=termite&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Suicidal defensive behaviour by frontal gland dehiscence in ''Globitermes sulphureus'' Haviland soldiers (Isoptera)|first1=C.|last2=Robert|first2=A.|date=1997|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s000400050049|volume=44|pages=289–297|last3=Van Tuyen|first3=V.|last4=Peppuy|first4=A.|last1=Bordereau}}</ref>。''[[Neocapriterme_taracua|Neocapriterme taracua]]'' 也會透過自殺來防禦，工蟻會擠壓背部表皮下的腺體，釋放出可以麻痺並殺死敵人的液體<ref>{{cite journal|title=Explosive backpacks in old termite workers|first1=J.|last2=Bourguignon|first2=T.|date=2012|journal=Science|issue=6093|doi=10.1126/science.1219129|volume=337|pages=436|bibcode=2012Sci...337..436S|pmid=22837520|last3=Hanus|first3=R.|last4=Demianova|first4=Z.|last5=Pytelkova|first5=J.|last6=Mares|first6=M.|last7=Foltynova|first7=P.|last8=Preisler|first8=J.|last9=Cvacka|first9=J.|first11=Y.|last11=Roisin|first10=J.|last10=Krasulova|last1=Sobotnik}}</ref>。新熱帶的[[齒白蟻科|齒白蟻科]]也會自爆，兵蟻在通道中受攻擊時會釋放液體，形成路障阻止入侵者<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Structure and function of defensive glands in soldiers of ''Glossotermes oculatus'' (Isoptera: Serritermitidae)|first1=J.|last2=Bourguignon|first2=T.|journal=Biological Journal of the Linnean Society|issue=4|doi=10.1111/j.1095-8312.2010.01392.x|year=2010|volume=99|pages=839–848|last3=Hanus|first3=R.|last4=Weyda|first4=F.|last5=Roisin|first5=Y.|last1=ŠobotnÍk}}</ref>。

面對屍體時工蟻會採取數種不同的策略，如掩蓋屍體、吃掉屍體，還有避開屍體<ref>{{cite journal|title=Evidence of cue synergism in termite corpse response behavior|first1=M.D.|last2=Shelton|first2=T.G.|date=2011|journal=Naturwissenschaften|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s00114-011-0871-3|volume=99|pages=89–93|bibcode=2012NW.....99...89U|pmid=22167071|last1=Ulyshen}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Response of the Formosan subterranean termites (Isoptera: Rhinotermitidae) to baits or nonrepellent termiticides in extended foraging arenas.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-entomology_2005-12_98_6/page/2143|first1=N.Y.|date=2005|journal=Journal of Economic Entomology|issue=6|doi=10.1603/0022-0493-98.6.2143|volume=98|pages=2143–2152|pmid=16539144|last1=Su}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Differential undertaking response of a lower termite to congeneric and conspecific corpses|first1=Q.|last2=Haynes|first2=K.F.|date=2013|journal=Scientific Reports|doi=10.1038/srep01650|volume=3|pages=1650|bibcode=2013NatSR...3E1650S|pmc=3629736|pmid=23598990|last3=Zhou|first3=X.|last1=Sun}}</ref>。白蟻會把屍體帶離巢穴丟棄（{{tsl|en|necrophoresis||necrophoresis}}） 來避免病原體擴散<ref name="termnecro">{{cite journal|title=Do termites avoid carcasses? behavioral responses depend on the nature of the carcasses|first1=K.-B.|last2=Yeap|first2=B.-K.|date=2012|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=4|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0036375|volume=7|pages=e36375|bibcode=2012PLoSO...736375N|pmc=3338677|pmid=22558452|last3=Tsunoda|first3=K.|last4=Yoshimura|first4=T.|last5=Lee|first5=C.Y.|last6=Korb|first6=J.|last1=Neoh}}</ref>。處理屍體的方式取決於屍體的狀態（如死亡時間）<ref name="termnecro" />。

=== 與其他生物的交互關係 ===
[[File:Rhizanthella_gardneri_—_Fred_Hort.jpg|链接=https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Rhizanthella_gardneri_%E2%80%94_Fred_Hort.jpg]]（''Rhizanthella gardneri'' ）是唯一由白蟻授粉的蘭花。]]
有一類真菌會偽裝成白蟻的卵，藉此避免天敵，這些真菌不會危害到白蟻的卵，有時候白蟻把這些真菌當卵照顧<ref>{{cite journal|title=Termite-egg mimicry by a sclerotium-forming fungus|first1=K.|date=2006|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|issue=1591|doi=10.1098/rspb.2005.3434|volume=273|pages=1203–1209|pmc=1560272|pmid=16720392|last1=Matsuura}}</ref>，這些真菌透過分泌[[葡糖苷酶|葡糖苷酶]]來偽裝成白蟻卵<ref>{{cite journal|title=Cuckoo fungus mimics termite eggs by producing the cellulose-digesting enzyme β-glucosidase|first1=K.|last2=Yashiro|first2=T.|date=2009|journal=Current Biology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.cub.2008.11.030|volume=19|pages=30–36|pmid=19110429|last3=Shimizu|first3=K.|last4=Tatsumi|first4=S.|last5=Tamura|first5=T.|last1=Matsuura}}</ref>。''[[Trichopsenius|Trichopsenius]]'' 屬的甲蟲會偽裝成[[散白蚁属|散白蟻]]，這些甲蟲會合成和白蟻一樣的表皮碳氫化合物，藉此混入蟻群中<ref>{{cite journal|title=Chemical mimicry as an integrating mechanism: cuticular hydrocarbons of a termitophile and its host|first1=R.W.|last2=McDaniel|first2=C.A.|date=1980|journal=Science|issue=4468|doi=10.1126/science.210.4468.431|volume=210|pages=431–433|bibcode=1980Sci...210..431H|pmid=17837424|last3=Blomquist|first3=G.J.|last1=Howard}}</ref>。''[[Austrospirachtha_mimetes|Austrospirachtha mimetes]]'' 的腹部特化膨大，讓這種甲蟲可以偽裝成白蟻工蟻<ref>{{cite journal|title=''Austrospirachtha mimetes'' a new termitophilous corotocine from Northern Australia (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae)|first1=J.A.L.|date=1973|journal=Australian Journal of Entomology|issue=4|doi=10.1111/j.1440-6055.1973.tb01678.x|volume=12|pages=307–310|last1=Watson}}</ref>。

有些螞蟻會將白蟻制服而不是直接殺死白蟻，這樣可以讓白蟻保持新鮮，''[[Formica_nigra|Formica nigra]]'' 就有這種行為<ref>{{cite journal|title=Termites Kept in Captivity by Ants|first1=H.O.|date=1878|journal=Nature|issue=471|doi=10.1038/019004b0|volume=19|pages=4–5|bibcode=1878Natur..19....4F|last1=Forbes}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。有些針蟻亞科的物種會成群結隊掠奪白蟻巢，有些物種則會單獨行動，偷食白蟻的卵或若蟲<ref name="arb" />。 ''Megaponera analis'' 會攻擊地上的蟻塚，而[[矛蚁亚科|矛蟻亞科]]則會攻擊地下蟻巢<ref name="arb" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Attacks by doryline ants and termite nest defences (Hymenoptera; Formicidae; Isoptera; Termitidae)|first1=J.|date=1985|journal=Sociobiology|volume=11|pages=189–200|last1=Darlington}}</ref>。除了敵對關係以外，有些物種也會跟白蟻和平共處，如 ''{{tsl|en|Nasutitermes corniger||Nasutitermes corniger}}'' 會和某些螞蟻形成交互關係，避免受專食白蟻的螞蟻襲擊<ref>{{cite journal|title=Behavioural Interactions Between ''Crematogaster brevispinosa rochai'' Forel (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) and Two Nasutitermes Species (Isoptera: Termitidae)|author=Quinet Y, Tekule N & de Biseau JC|journal=Journal of Insect Behavior|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s10905-005-9343-y|year=2005|volume=18|pages=1–17}}</ref>。已知最早的白蟻螞蟻交互關係是阿茲特克蟻（''{{tsl|en|Azteca (genus)||Azteca}}''）和象白蟻（''Nasutitermes'' ），年代為渐新世至中新世<ref>{{cite journal|title=The First Ant-Termite Syninclusion in Amber with CT-Scan Analysis of Taphonomy|first1=D.|last2=Aria|first2=C.|date=2014|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=8|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0104410|volume=9|pages=e104410|bibcode=2014PLoSO...9j4410C|pmc=4139309|pmid=25140873|last3=Garrouste|first3=R.|last4=Wils|first4=P.|last5=Legendre|first5=F.|last6=Nel|first6=A.|last7=Korb|first7=J.|last1=Coty}}</ref>。
[[File:Megaponera_analis_raid_collecting_termites.jpg|左]]
有 54 種螞蟻被記錄到居住在象白蟻廢棄的或使用中的蟻巢裡<ref name="santos2010">{{cite journal|title=Ant fauna (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) associated to arboreal nests of Nasutitermes spp: (Isoptera, Termitidae) in a cacao plantation in southeastern Bahia, Brazil|first1=P.P.|last2=Vasconcellos|first2=A.|date=2010|journal=Revista Brasileira de Entomologia|issue=3|doi=10.1590/S0085-56262010000300016|volume=54|pages=450–454|last3=Jahyny|first3=B.|last4=Delabie|first4=J.H.C.|last1=Santos}}</ref>，這麼多種螞蟻會居住在象白蟻蟻巢中是因為它們的活動範圍高度重疊，另外，居住在象白蟻蟻巢中可以躲避洪水<ref name="santos2010" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=Trophic Interactions Between Ants and Termites that Share Common Nests|first1=K.|last2=Ramos|first2=C.|date=1995|journal=Annals of the Entomological Society of America|issue=3|doi=10.1093/aesa/88.3.328|volume=88|pages=328–333|last3=Issa|first3=S.|last1=Jaffe}}</ref>。[[虹琉璃蟻屬|虹琉璃蟻屬]]也會居住在白蟻巢內，但兩者之間除了掠食以外沒有任何交互關係<ref name="wheeler1936" />。少數幾種的白蟻會居住在螞蟻巢內<ref>{{cite journal|title=A Revision of the fire ants, ''Solenopsis geminata'' group (Hymenoptera: Formicidae: Myrmicinae)|first1=J.C.|date=1991|journal=Journal of the New York Entomological Society|issue=2|doi=10.5281/zenodo.24912|volume=99|pages=141–198|jstor=25009890|last1=Trager}}</ref>。很多類群的無脊椎動物都是白蟻的蟻客，如某些甲蟲、馬陸、蠅類和蜈蚣，這些蟻客居住在白蟻群體內，離開白蟻群體便無法存活<ref name="Britannica2" />，有些甲蟲和蠅類具有特化腺體，可分泌物質吸引白蟻照顧它們。鳥類、蜥蜴、蛇和蠍子也會居住在白蟻丘之中<ref name="Britannica2" />。

有些白蟻會搬運花粉，也會頻繁地訪花<ref name="Cingel">{{cite book|last1=Cingel|first1=N.A. van der|title=An atlas of orchid pollination: America, Africa, Asia and Australia|date=2001|publisher=Balkema|location=Rotterdam|isbn=978-90-5410-486-5|page=224}}</ref>，所以白蟻被認為是某些植物的授粉者<ref>{{cite web|title=Orchid Pollination: exploring a fascinating world|url=http://staugorchidsociety.org/PDF/OrchidPollinationbyRonMcHatton.pdf|accessdate=5 September 2015|date=2011|publisher=The American Orchid Society|last1=McHatton|first1=R.|page=344|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183240/https://www.staugorchidsociety.org/PDF/OrchidPollinationbyRonMcHatton.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，尤其是主要由白蟻授粉的[[地下兰|地下蘭]]（''Rhizanthella gardneri''），地下蘭是唯一由白蟻授粉的[[蘭科|蘭花]]<ref name="Cingel" />。

很多植物具有特化的機制可以抵擋白蟻攻擊，然而植物在種子階段很脆弱，因為防禦機制要等到發芽以後才會開始發育<ref>{{cite book|last1=Cowie|first1=R.|title=Journey to a Waterfall a biologist in Africa|date=2014|publisher=Lulu Press|location=Raleigh, North Carolina|isbn=978-1-304-66939-1|page=169}}</ref>。植物抵禦白蟻的機制通常是在細胞壁中分泌忌避性的物質<ref name="envirostud">{{cite book|last1=Tan|first1=K.H.|title=Environmental Soil Science|date=2009|publisher=CRC Press|location=Boca Raton, Florida|isbn=978-1-4398-9501-6|pages=105–106|edition=3rd}}</ref>，這種物質可以降低白蟻分解纖維素的效率。澳洲有一種產品就是用植物萃取物做的，這種產品的使用方式是在建物的周圍塗一圈以形成防護圈<ref name="envirostud" />。一種由澳洲[[玄参属|玄參屬]]萃取出的物質對白蟻具有忌避性<ref name="abc2005">{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200511/s1507502.htm|title=Plant extract stops termites dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090615163604/http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200511/s1507502.htm|first=Sarah|last=Clark|newspaper=ABC|archivedate=15 June 2009|date=15 November 2005|accessdate=8 February 2014}}</ref>。研究顯示白蟻會拒絕取食含有忌避性物質的食物，最後餓死，如果把白蟻和忌避物放在一起，白蟻會四處亂竄最後死亡<ref name="abc2005" />。

=== 與環境的關係 ===
白蟻的數量會受到人類活動及其他因子影響。一篇研究指出人類活動越高、樹木和土壤覆蓋率越低、牲畜和山羊數量越多的地區，白蟻的數量越少，尤其是食木的白蟻<ref name="termiteassemblages2010">{{cite journal|title=Termite assemblages in three habitats under different disturbance regimes in the semi-arid Caatinga of NE Brazil|first1=Alexandre|last2=Bandeira|first2=Adelmar G.|date=February 2010|journal=Journal of Arid Environments|publisher=Elsevier|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.jaridenv.2009.07.007|volume=74|pages=298–302|bibcode=2010JArEn..74..298V|issn=0140-1963|last3=Moura|first3=Flávia Maria S.|last4=Araújo|first4=Virgínia Farias P.|last5=Gusmão|first5=Maria Avany B.|last6=Reginaldo|first6=Constantino|last1=Vasconcellos}}</ref>。

== 蟻巢 ==
[[File:Termite-nest-Tulum-Mexico.jpg|替代=Photograph of an arboreal termite nest built on a tree trunk high above ground. It has an ovoid shape and appears to be larger than a basketball. It is dark brown in colour, and it is made of carton, a mixture of digested wood and termite faeces that is strong and resistant to rain. Covered tunnels constructed of carton can be seen leading down the shaded side of the tree from the nest to the ground.]]
[[File:Termitenest33189014241_9f0022ebfe_o.jpg|缩略图]][[棕櫚海灘|棕梠海灘]]。]]
蟻巢可粗分為三類：地下型（完全在土中）、出土型（凸出地表）、樹棲型（巢體不接觸到地面，但有連接到地面的蟻道<ref name="woodregulation">{{cite book|last1=Noirot|first1=C.|last2=Darlington|first2=J.P.E.C.|title=''Termite Nests: Architecture, Regulation and Defence'' in Termites: Evolution, Sociality, Symbioses, Ecology|date=2000|publisher=Springer|doi=10.1007/978-94-017-3223-9_6|isbn=978-94-017-3223-9|pages=121–139}}</ref>）。出土型蟻巢是由土壤與泥巴建築而成{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=20}}。蟻巢可提供適宜的居住環境並保護白蟻不受天敵捕食。大部分的蟻巢是地下型的<ref name="divterm">{{cite journal|title=The Diversity, Abundance and Biomass of Termites under Differing Levels of Disturbance in the Mbalmayo Forest Reserve, Southern Cameroon|first1=P.|last2=Bignell|first2=D.E.|date=1996|journal=Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|issue=1335|doi=10.1098/rstb.1996.0004|volume=351|pages=51–68|bibcode=1996RSPTB.351...51E|last3=Sands|first3=W.A.|last4=Mawdsley|first4=N. A.|last5=Lawton|first5=J. H.|last6=Wood|first6=T.G.|last7=Bignell|first7=N.C.|last1=Eggleton}}</ref>。較為原始的白蟻築巢於木製結構中，如倒木、樹樁，和活樹死去的組織之中，正如同它們百萬年前的祖先一般<ref name="woodregulation" />。

白蟻巢主要以糞便構成，糞便是很合適的建材{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=21}}，除了糞便外，樹棲型白蟻築巢時也會加入消化過的植物組織，這種類型的巢材質類似紙板，地下白蟻則會加入泥土來築巢和建築蟻塚。並非所有的白蟻巢都很顯眼，有些蟻巢，如熱帶雨林中的蟻巢便是建在地底下<ref name="divterm" />，如 [[Apicotermitinae|Apicotermitinae]] 亞科{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=21}}。居住在木頭中的白蟻會在取食的同時慢慢挖出隧道並居住於其中。蟻巢和蟻塚可以讓柔軟的白蟻免於脫水、光照、病原菌和寄生蟲，並保護白蟻不受天敵攻擊<ref>{{cite journal|title=Trophic interactions among invertebrates in termitaria in the African savanna: a stable isotope approach|url=http://mediatum.ub.tum.de/node?id=681224|first1=S.N.|last2=Freymann|first2=B.P.|date=2008|journal=Ecological Entomology|issue=6|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2311.2008.01029.x|volume=33|pages=758–764|last3=Schnyder|first3=H.|last1=De Visse|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411183256/http://mediatum.ub.tum.de/node?id=681224|dead-url=no}}</ref>。樹棲型蟻巢材質通常較為脆弱，因此當蟻巢受到侵襲時，白蟻會反擊掠食者{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=22}}。

紅樹林沼澤中的象白蟻會築樹棲巢，該巢富含木質素，且含有少量纖維素和木聚醣，這是因為象白蟻的腸道內有細菌可以幫助他們分解纖維素，而象白蟻會用糞便築巢，並將分解後的物質一起鑲入巢中。在波多黎各的紅樹林沼澤中，樹棲型白蟻巢可佔的地上總體碳含量的 2 %，這些蟻巢主要成分為部分分解的木材組織，來自於紅樹林樹種的樹幹與枝條，這些樹種包含 ''{{tsl|en|Rhizophora mangle||Rhizophora mangle}}''（紅樹）、''{{tsl|en|Avicennia germinans||Avicennia germinans}}''（黑紅樹）和 ''[[Laguncularia_racemose|Laguncularia racemose]]''（白紅樹<ref name="Vane_et_al_2013">{{cite journal|title=Degradation of mangrove tissues by arboreal termites (''Nasutitermes acajutlae'') and their role in the mangrove C cycle (Puerto Rico): Chemical characterization and organic matter provenance using bulk δ13C, C/N, alkaline CuO oxidation-GC/MS, and solid-state|url=http://nora.nerc.ac.uk/503347/1/ggge20194.pdf|first1=C.H.|last2=Kim|first2=A.W.|date=2013|journal=Geochemistry, Geophysics, Geosystems|issue=8|doi=10.1002/ggge.20194|volume=14|pages=3176–3191|bibcode=2013GGG....14.3176V|last3=Moss-Hayes|first3=V.|last4=Snape|first4=C.E.|last5=Diaz|first5=M.C.|last6=Khan|first6=N.S.|last7=Engelhart|first7=S.E.|last8=Horton|first8=B.P.|last1=Vane|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007120907/http://nora.nerc.ac.uk/503347/1/ggge20194.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>）。

有些物種會建築錯綜複雜且數量較多的巢，這種行為稱作「多巢型（polycalism）」，這些散布的巢會透過地下腔室彼此連接<ref name="wilson2014" />。''[[Apicotermes|Apicotermes]]'' 和 ''{{tsl|en|Trinervitermes||Trinervitermes}}'' 便是多巢型的物種<ref name="nasupol">{{cite journal|title=Reproductive mechanisms in termites: Polycalism and polygyny in ''Nasutitermes polygynus'' and ''N. costalis''|first1=Y.|last2=Pasteels|first2=J. M.|date=1986|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=2|doi=10.1007/BF02224595|volume=33|pages=149–167|last1=Roisin}}</ref>。建築蟻塚的物種很少是多巢型的，而樹棲型的象白蟻有少數幾個物種被觀察到具有多巢型的現象<ref name="nasupol" />。

=== 蟻塚 ===
凸出地表的蟻巢被稱作蟻塚{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=21}}，蟻塚可以提供比蟻巢更完備的庇護{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=22}}。多雨地區的蟻塚會受到雨水侵蝕，因其材料富含黏土，而樹棲型蟻巢則可忍受雨水沖打{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=21}}。蟻塚的特定區域特別設計來抵禦外敵，如 ''[[Cubitermes|Cubitermes]]'' 會建築狹窄的通道，通道的直徑剛好可以讓兵蟻堵住<ref>{{cite journal|title=The structure of gallery networks in the nests of termite ''Cubitermes'' spp. revealed by X-ray tomography.|first1=A.|last2=Jost|first2=C.|date=2008|journal=Die Naturwissenschaften|issue=9|doi=10.1007/s00114-008-0388-6|volume=95|pages=877–884|bibcode=2008NW.....95..877P|pmid=18493731|last3=Couturier|first3=E.|last4=Valverde|first4=S.|last5=Douady|first5=S.|last6=Theraulaz|first6=G.|last1=Perna}}</ref>。王室是蟻王蟻后居住的地方，其外壁非常堅硬，是蟻塚的最後一道防線{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=22}}。

[[大白蟻屬|大白蟻屬]]（''Macrotermes'' ）的某些物種可以築出巨大的蟻塚{{sfn|Bignell|Roisin|Lo|2010|p=21}}，可高達 8 至 9 公尺<ref name="Britannica2" />。''{{tsl|en|Amitermes meridionalis||Amitermes meridionalis}}'' 可築出高 3 至 4 公尺，寬 2.5 公尺的蟻塚。世上最高的蟻塚位於[[刚果民主共和国|剛果]]，高度為 12.8 公尺<ref>{{Cite book|title=Guinness World Records 2014|last=Glenday|first=Craig|year=2014|isbn=978-1-908843-15-9|location=|pages=[https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_r3e7/page/33 33]|quote=|via=|url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec0000unse_r3e7/page/33}}</ref>。

有的蟻塚外型很特別，如磁白蟻（''Amitermes''），磁白蟻的蟻塚向南北延伸，外形扁平<ref name="jacklyn1991">{{cite journal|title=Evidence for Adaptive Variation in the Orientation of ''Amitermes'' (Isoptera, Termitinae) Mounds From Northern Australia|first1=P.|date=1991|journal=Australian Journal of Zoology|issue=5|doi=10.1071/ZO9910569|volume=39|pages=569|last1=Jacklyn}}</ref><ref name="jacklyn2002">{{cite journal|title=Evidence for the use of magnetic cues in mound construction by the termite ''Amitermes meridionalis'' (Isoptera : Termitinae)|first1=P.M.|last2=Munro|first2=U.|date=2002|journal=Australian Journal of Zoology|issue=4|doi=10.1071/ZO01061|volume=50|pages=357|last1=Jacklyn}}</ref>，這種蟻塚可以在清晨時快速吸收陽光提高溫度，並在日正當中時避免吸收過多陽光導致過熱，中午過後的溫度維持穩定，直到黃昏太陽下山時<ref>{{cite journal|title=Some Consequences of the Shape and Orientation of 'magnetic' Termite Mounds|url=http://espace.library.uq.edu.au/view/UQ:10143/gg_ajz_21_73.pdf|first1=G.C.|date=1973|journal=Australian Journal of Zoology|issue=2|doi=10.1071/ZO9730231|volume=21|pages=231–237|last1=Grigg}}</ref>。<gallery widths="200" class="center">
